Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.21,0:04:34.92,ExtraSciFi - EN,,0,0,0,,Shelley explores this trope
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.21,0:04:34.92,ExtraSciFi - 中文,,0,0,0,,雪莱对这一隐喻的探索
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.92,0:04:38.12,ExtraSciFi - EN,,0,0,0,,far more thoroughly than many who would eventually borrow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.92,0:04:38.12,ExtraSciFi - 中文,,0,0,0,,远比许多后来者深刻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.26,0:04:40.33,ExtraSciFi - EN,,0,0,0,,The monster, outwardly ugly,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.26,0:04:40.33,ExtraSciFi - 中文,,0,0,0,,外表丑陋的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.33,0:04:44.89,ExtraSciFi - EN,,0,0,0,,finds itself continuously rejected by an inwardly ugly humanity,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.33,0:04:44.89,ExtraSciFi - 中文,,0,0,0,,发现自己不断遭受内心丑陋的人类排斥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.95,0:04:46.98,ExtraSciFi - EN,,0,0,0,,rejected at birth by Victor,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.95,0:04:46.98,ExtraSciFi - 中文,,0,0,0,,诞生时被维克多抛弃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.98,0:04:49.28,ExtraSciFi - EN,,0,0,0,,attacked in the first village he visited,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.98,0:04:49.28,ExtraSciFi - 中文,,0,0,0,,进入第一个村庄时受到攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.28,0:04:52.01,ExtraSciFi - EN,,0,0,0,,turned away by the cottagers he cared for
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.28,0:04:52.01,ExtraSciFi - 中文,,0,0,0,,被喜欢的村民驱逐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.08,0:04:55.93,ExtraSciFi - EN,,0,0,0,,and thus, at last, the monster turns on humanity itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.08,0:04:55.93,ExtraSciFi - 中文,,0,0,0,,因此，怪物终于开始仇视人类
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.05,0:04:57.87,ExtraSciFi - EN,,0,0,0,,This theme of rejection
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.05,0:04:57.87,ExtraSciFi - 中文,,0,0,0,,这一主题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.87,0:05:02.27,ExtraSciFi - EN,,0,0,0,,despite offering the best intentions and offering something truly of worth,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.87,0:05:02.27,ExtraSciFi - 中文,,0,0,0,,即，尽管表示了最大的善意，奉献了真正宝贵的东西，却依旧遭人排斥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.30,0:05:05.20,ExtraSciFi - EN,,0,0,0,,has become not only a theme of science fiction literature
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.30,0:05:05.20,ExtraSciFi - 中文,,0,0,0,,不单单存在于科幻文学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.20,0:05:07.89,ExtraSciFi - EN,,0,0,0,,but of the geek culture that has grown up around it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.20,0:05:07.89,ExtraSciFi - 中文,,0,0,0,,也存在于由其衍生的极客文化
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.10,0:05:10.97,ExtraSciFi - EN,,0,0,0,,But part of the reason that we see nobility in the monster
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.10,0:05:10.97,ExtraSciFi - 中文,,0,0,0,,然而我们觉得这个怪物高尚，部分是出于
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.97,0:05:15.07,ExtraSciFi - EN,,0,0,0,,is that we see it self-educate, reading the greatest books of the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.97,0:05:15.07,ExtraSciFi - 中文,,0,0,0,,我们看到它自我学习，阅读过去的名著
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.21,0:05:19.91,ExtraSciFi - EN,,0,0,0,,Mary Shelley saw her work as part of an ongoing tradition of Western literature.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.21,0:05:19.91,ExtraSciFi - 中文,,0,0,0,,玛丽·雪莱将自己的作品视为西方文学传统的延续
